import React from 'react'
import { Row,Form,Button } from 'react-bootstrap'

const FormInput = () => {
  return (
   <Row>
     <Form className="d-flex p-3 ">
      <Form.Group sm="4" className="mb-3 m-2" controlId="formBasicEmail">
       
        <Form.Control type="email" placeholder="اضافه سؤال" />
        
      </Form.Group>

      <Form.Group sm="4" className="mb-3 m-2" controlId="formBasicPassword">
        
        <Form.Control type="password" placeholder="اضافه اجابه" />
      </Form.Group>
      
      <Button sm="4" className="btn btn-primary m-2" type="submit">
        اضافه
      </Button>
    </Form>
   </Row>
  )
}

export default FormInput
